Software
========

[libsixel](https://github.com/saitoha/libsixel)
-----------------------------------------------
Encoder/Decoder implementation for DEC SIXEL graphics.

[tanasinn](http://zuse.jp/tanasinn)
-----------------------------------
A terminal emulator extension for Gecko-based applications.

[Sentimental-SKK](http://saitoha.github.com/sentimental-skk/)
-------------------------------------------------------------
A Japanese Input Method SKK (Simple Kana to Kanji conversion) program

[trachet](http://saitoha.github.com/trachet/)
---------------------------------------------
Terminal I/O step-by-step debugger

[mouseterm-plus](https://github.com/saitoha/mouseterm-plus)
-------------------------------------------
Experimental fork of [brodie's mouseterm](https://bitheap.org/mouseterm/)

[Haisyo](https://github.com/saitoha/Haisyo)
-------------------------------------------
拝承

Other Open source contributions
===============================

I contributed more or less to the following software:

    - iTerm2
    - vim
    - tmux
    - mouseterm
    - poderosa
    - xterm
    - mlterm
    - yaft
